    "bio": "Boost your customer engagement with 2Chat, the leading enterprise-grade WhatsApp communication platform! Seamlessly integrate WhatsApp Business API for multi-agent teamwork and automate sales, marketing, and support with ease. Connect to HubSpot, Zapier, and more for targeted campaigns that drive results. Scalable, secure, and loaded with free tools like a WhatsApp Number Checker, 2Chat’s powerful analytics fuel business growth. Transform communication today! ",
    "verified": false,
